George Shibata https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/George_Shibata 0 George Shibata (November 14, 1926 in Garland, Utah – May 20, 1987 in Huntington Beach, California) was an American actor and the first Asian American graduate of the United States Military Academy, Class of 1951.
